Company Overview of Waverton Investment Management Ltd.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Waverton Investment Management Ltd. is a privately owned investment manager. The firm provides its services to high net worth clients, family offices, trusts, charities, investment companies, pension and profit sharing plans, pooled investment vehicles, charitable organizations, endowments, and corporations. It manages separate client-focused equity, fixed income, and balanced portfolios. The firm also manages mutual funds, hedge funds, charities, and other specialist investment portfolios for its clients. It invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe. The firm also makes alternative investments. It operates as a subsidiary of Credit Suisse. The firm was formerly ...
Waverton Investment Management Ltd. is a privately owned investment manager. The firm provides its services to high net worth clients, family offices, trusts, charities, investment companies, pension and profit sharing plans, pooled investment vehicles, charitable organizations, endowments, and corporations. It manages separate client-focused equity, fixed income, and balanced portfolios. The firm also manages mutual funds, hedge funds, charities, and other specialist investment portfolios for its clients. It invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe. The firm also makes alternative investments. It operates as a subsidiary of Credit Suisse. The firm was formerly known as J O Hambro Investment Management Limited. It was founded in 1986 and is based in London, United Kingdom. Waverton Investment Management Ltd. operates as a subsidiary of JOHIM CS Limited.
Detailed Description


