Key Personnel
The investment of our client portfolios and funds is the responsibility of a team of highly experienced investment professionals. The team has on average over 20 years of individual investment experience and many have worked together for a number of years.
We place the same emphasis on management and support functions. Whether involved in the day to day management of the business, or in the direct administration of our clients’ portfolios, high standards of industry experience and practical knowledge are central to our team approach.




