5. Cookies. Cookies are small text files that help us make your experience on Waverton.co.uk better. More information about how we use cookies can be found on our Privacy Policy. Although cookies are nothing new, we now need your consent to use cookies. If you don’t want us to use cookies, some parts of the site will not work. By using any part of the site you consent to the use of cookies. Alternatively, you can let us know whether you accept cookies by Accepting below.
