Search









 

Investment Funds
Waverton Funds is a range of investment vehicles, with each strategy managed by a dedicated specialist team. The range includes 12 equity, fixed income and multi-asset funds. All of Waverton's fund managers are active, fundamental long-only stock pickers who invest with conviction for the long-term.
At Waverton, the managers of these investment funds operate within a wider collaborative group of over thirty experienced investment professionals. This provides an excellent environment for sharing ideas and insights across geographies and asset classes, whilst allowing each fund team to focus on delivering its objectives for investors.


